# .cursorrules - Production Guardrails for IG_Agent_v29.1

[Architecture Priorities]
CorePipeline=src/trading/trading_loop.py -> src/trading/environment_scorer.py -> src/signals/signal_engine.py -> src/trading/points_engine.py -> src/execution/risk_manager.py
SpecReference=IG_Agent_v29.1_COMPLETE_SPEC.md and docs/V29.1_ARCHITECTURE.md are authoritative for v29.1 behaviour
DatabaseRetention=Do NOT alter or touch SQLite history tables, JSON schema fallback structures, or relative log paths on disk without explicit operator request.

[Strict Safety Constraints]
TradingMathGuard=NEVER modify hard risk limits (max_daily_loss_gbp, REST budget, instance lock semantics) without spec update.
RefactoringDepth=Restrict structural edits to isolated fixes with test coverage. Prefer extending open_position_view, learning_trade_policy, protective_learning over rewriting trading_loop.

[Multi-Agent Delegation Roles]
ArchitectAgent=Focus on snapshot/P&L data flow, learning plane boundaries, config merge chain (v29 -> v25).
WorkerAgent=Focus on isolated patches, tests in tests/, dashboard dist rebuild after JSX changes.
